            <p class="destination_p">
                Corniche Luxor:
                The picturesque Luxor Corniche, a promenade that stretches along the east bank of the Nile River, is a
                great
                place to unwind. Enjoy expansive views of the river and Luxor's West Bank, which is home to several
                historic
                tombs and temples. You can also observe the elegant sailing of classic feluccas on the glistening
